### 등록
POST http://localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "courseId": 105
}

### 유저 강좌 리스트 조회, ACTIVE만 조회
POST http://localhost:8080/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "status": "HIDDEN"
}


### 단일 강좌 조회(userId + courseId)
POST http://localhost:8080/detail
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "courseId": 103
}

### 상태 수정
PATCH http://localhost:8080/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "courseId": 103,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Progress 수정
PATCH http://localhost:8080/progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "courseId": 101,
  "progress": "TRUE"
}


### 삭제 (soft delete, userId + courseId 기준)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "courseId": 1016,
  "status": "REFUNDED"
}